<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Everything you need, <span class="handwritten">nothing you don't</span></h2>
      <p>Designed to feel like a real whiteboard, with all the flexibility of digital</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--yellow);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Natural Input</h3>
        <p>Type anywhere on your board and watch your text appear in beautiful handwritten fonts. Just like writing on a real whiteboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--orange);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strike to Complete</h3>
        <p>Draw a line through any task to mark it done. Scribble harder to delete it completely. It's that intuitive.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--green);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Daily Boards</h3>
        <p>Each day gets its own board. Navigate between days with ease. Your past plans are always there when you need them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--marker-blue);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multiple Fonts</h3>
        <p>Choose from 6 handwritten fonts to match your mood. From casual to architectural, find your perfect writing style.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--blue-border);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"></path>
            <path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Drawing Mode</h3>
        <p>Sketch, doodle, or annotate freely. Add arrows, circles, or whatever helps you think. Your board, your rules.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--dark-green);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Privacy First</h3>
        <p>Your plans stay on your computer. No accounts, no cloud, no tracking. Just you and your daily goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dark-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 span {
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: 1.1em;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--whiteboard);
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
  }

  .feature-card:nth-child(even) .feature-icon {
    transform: rotate(3deg);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark-blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>